{"tid":1578344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國本地文宣方向 - 雙重標準 及 反對通知書","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:19.000Z","uid":87915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa15420784d06ba09762662004a8d69d6aba2e78","tid":1578344,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"文宣 其中一個作用係比d 唔支持我地嘅人睇<br />\n<br />\n依家點解釋示威者暴力升級，不外乎兩個方向<br />\n<br />\n首先唔好意思，本人係首席冷氣軍師，英文又唔好，圖又唔多張，希望文宣組可以參考吓<br />\n<br />\n1. 警方雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n菜刀 vs 餐刀<br />\n見後生就拉  見老嘅就搭膊頭 放人<br />\nEtc<br />\n<br />\n一個例子 一張poster 形式<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n政府想利用反對通知書 去製造和平示威遊行嘅人少咗好多<br />\n好多外國人唔知，剩係會覺得少咗人<br />\n<br />\n要有張poster 長期用<br />\n反對通知書 違反基本法<br />\n限制香港人示威自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝文宣組"},{"pid":"9b3521065491a96dd334da729f22c6b204b3658e","tid":1578344,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7696f6f9a043b17d91c6a3f4f35579059703d7dc","tid":1578344,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"的確好多外國人唔知藍絲同白衫老黑做咩俾人打<br />\n要好好宣傳講清楚<br />\nReddit Twitter #Chinazi"},{"pid":"f840e53573ba27c73a4d946dbb6852affbf7616e","tid":1578344,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c8cc90fb9377d8c752ba8dc5a4457c50b94a06a","tid":1578344,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffbad382efd927d917ca9a1d16276af1e443a216","tid":1578344,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"reddit唔好俾link<br />\n直接入去search hong Kong post"},{"pid":"a6cd544aba2a38ce8545f9fd5bd4e2f5d48bc383","tid":1578344,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"35e7ddc4bf9929f17b8c877cf4e2b6cc42db5b2e","tid":1578344,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2beaf20216fceb2888d98ab9d3e272b7acc545c7","tid":1578344,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=a6d6c9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"e771fcbc56fc43357e2eae18d1c67eca4f657efa","tid":1578344,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eu1EKtq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEu1EKtq.jpg&h=b403d295&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/beqx4ts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbeqx4ts.jpg&h=3e57ced4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c32508c6b40717b4dc05a016f7af09cda4f6e18","tid":1578344,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"想要英文翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f786dea08a7c2a11777cb826546d2bf179978840","tid":1578344,"uid":221336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep8sig4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep8sig4.png&h=fb3bcb5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25fcc8188a61fd0f63aca483abb0d8c3e57d2b20","tid":1578344,"uid":273265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"[外地文宣] 認同課金買online Ads請進<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591272</a>"}]}